{"key":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01|Jas|4","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jas","chapter":4,"textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024","parserRevision":"v11","verses":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:4:1","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jas","bookOrder":58,"chapter":4,"verse":1,"text":"What is the source of wars and fights among you? Don’t they come from your passions that wage war within you?","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:4:2","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jas","bookOrder":58,"chapter":4,"verse":2,"text":"You desire and do not have. You murder and covet and cannot obtain. You fight and wage war. You do not have because you do not ask.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:4:3","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jas","bookOrder":58,"chapter":4,"verse":3,"text":"You ask and don’t receive because you ask with wrong motives, so that you may spend it on your pleasures.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:4:4","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jas","bookOrder":58,"chapter":4,"verse":4,"text":"You adulterous people! Don’t you know that friendship with the world is hostility toward God? So whoever wants to be the friend of the world becomes the enemy of God.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:4:5","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jas","bookOrder":58,"chapter":4,"verse":5,"text":"Or do you think it’s without reason that the Scripture says: The spirit he made to dwell in us envies intensely?","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:4:6","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jas","bookOrder":58,"chapter":4,"verse":6,"text":"But he gives greater grace. Therefore he says:","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:4:7","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jas","bookOrder":58,"chapter":4,"verse":7,"text":"Therefore, submit to God. Resist the devil, and he will flee from you.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:4:8","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jas","bookOrder":58,"chapter":4,"verse":8,"text":"Draw near to God, and he will draw near to you. Cleanse your hands, sinners, and purify your hearts, you double-minded.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:4:9","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jas","bookOrder":58,"chapter":4,"verse":9,"text":"Be miserable and mourn and weep. Let your laughter be turned to mourning and your joy to gloom.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:4:10","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jas","bookOrder":58,"chapter":4,"verse":10,"text":"Humble yourselves before the Lord, and he will exalt you.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:4:11","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jas","bookOrder":58,"chapter":4,"verse":11,"text":"Don’t criticize one another, brothers and sisters. Anyone who defames or judges a fellow believer defames and judges the law. If you judge the law, you are not a doer of the law but a judge.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:4:12","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jas","bookOrder":58,"chapter":4,"verse":12,"text":"There is one lawgiver and judge who is able to save and to destroy. But who are you to judge your neighbor?","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:4:13","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jas","bookOrder":58,"chapter":4,"verse":13,"text":"Come now, you who say, “Today or tomorrow we will travel to such and such a city and spend a year there and do business and make a profit.”","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:4:14","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jas","bookOrder":58,"chapter":4,"verse":14,"text":"Yet you do not know what tomorrow will bring —what your life will be! For you are like vapor that appears for a little while, then vanishes.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:4:15","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jas","bookOrder":58,"chapter":4,"verse":15,"text":"Instead, you should say, “If the Lord wills, we will live and do this or that.”","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:4:16","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jas","bookOrder":58,"chapter":4,"verse":16,"text":"But as it is, you boast in your arrogance. All such boasting is evil.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:4:17","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jas","bookOrder":58,"chapter":4,"verse":17,"text":"So it is sin to know the good and yet not do it.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"}],"layout":{"bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jas","chapter":4,"paragraphStarts":[1,4,6,7,11,13,15],"headings":[{"beforeVerse":1,"text":"Proud or Humble"},{"beforeVerse":13,"text":"Our Will and God’s Will"}],"poetryBlocks":[],"studyByVerse":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:4:1","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"What is the source of wars and fights among you? Don’t they come from your passions "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 7:23","book":"Rom","chapter":7,"verse":23,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ti 3:9","book":"Tit","chapter":3,"verse":9,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" that wage war within you? "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or war in your members"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 7:23","book":"Rom","chapter":7,"verse":23},{"label":"Ti 3:9","book":"Tit","chapter":3,"verse":9}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or war in your members"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:4:2","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"You desire and do not have. You murder and covet and cannot obtain. You fight and wage war. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Or You desire and do not have, so you murder. You covet and cannot obtain, so you fight and wage war."},{"kind":"text","text":" You do not have because you do not ask. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":2,"text":"Or You desire and do not have, so you murder. You covet and cannot obtain, so you fight and wage war."}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:4:3","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"You ask and don’t receive because you ask with wrong motives, so that you may spend it on your pleasures. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 18:41","book":"Psa","chapter":18,"verse":41,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Jn 3:22","book":"1Jn","chapter":3,"verse":22,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Jn 5:14","book":"1Jn","chapter":5,"verse":14,"letter":"c"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ps 18:41","book":"Psa","chapter":18,"verse":41},{"label":"1Jn 3:22","book":"1Jn","chapter":3,"verse":22},{"label":"1Jn 5:14","book":"1Jn","chapter":5,"verse":14}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:4:4","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"You adulterous people! "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit Adulteresses"},{"kind":"text","text":" Don’t you know that friendship with the world is hostility toward God? So whoever wants to be the friend of the world becomes the enemy of God. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 15:19","book":"Jhn","chapter":15,"verse":19,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jms 1:27","book":"Jas","chapter":1,"verse":27,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Jn 2:15","book":"1Jn","chapter":2,"verse":15,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jn 15:19","book":"Jhn","chapter":15,"verse":19},{"label":"Jms 1:27","book":"Jas","chapter":1,"verse":27},{"label":"1Jn 2:15","book":"1Jn","chapter":2,"verse":15}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit Adulteresses"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:4:5","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Or do you think it’s without reason that the Scripture says: The spirit he made to dwell in us envies intensely? "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Or Scripture says: He jealously yearns for the spirit he made to live in us?, or Scripture says: The Spirit he made to dwell in us longs jealously?"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 6:19","book":"1Co","chapter":6,"verse":19,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Co 6:16","book":"2Co","chapter":6,"verse":16,"letter":"b"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Co 6:19","book":"1Co","chapter":6,"verse":19},{"label":"2Co 6:16","book":"2Co","chapter":6,"verse":16}],"footnotes":[{"marker":2,"text":"Or Scripture says: He jealously yearns for the spirit he made to live in us?, or Scripture says: The Spirit he made to dwell in us longs jealously?"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:4:6","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But he gives greater grace. Therefore he says:"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:4:7","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Therefore, submit to God. Resist the devil, and he will flee from you. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 4:27","book":"Eph","chapter":4,"verse":27,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 6:11","book":"Eph","chapter":6,"verse":11,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 5:8","book":"1Pe","chapter":5,"verse":8,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Eph 4:27","book":"Eph","chapter":4,"verse":27},{"label":"Eph 6:11","book":"Eph","chapter":6,"verse":11},{"label":"1Pt 5:8","book":"1Pe","chapter":5,"verse":8}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:4:8","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Draw near to God, and he will draw near to you. Cleanse your hands, sinners, and purify your hearts, you double-minded. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Ch 15:2","book":"2Ch","chapter":15,"verse":2,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 1:16","book":"Isa","chapter":1,"verse":16,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jms 1:8","book":"Jas","chapter":1,"verse":8,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"2Ch 15:2","book":"2Ch","chapter":15,"verse":2},{"label":"Is 1:16","book":"Isa","chapter":1,"verse":16},{"label":"Jms 1:8","book":"Jas","chapter":1,"verse":8}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:4:9","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Be miserable and mourn and weep. Let your laughter be turned to mourning and your joy to gloom. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 5:4","book":"Mat","chapter":5,"verse":4,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 6:25","book":"Luk","chapter":6,"verse":25,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 5:4","book":"Mat","chapter":5,"verse":4},{"label":"Lk 6:25","book":"Luk","chapter":6,"verse":25}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:4:10","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Humble yourselves before the Lord, and he will exalt you."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:4:11","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Don’t criticize one another, brothers and sisters. Anyone who defames or judges a fellow believer "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or his brother or sister"},{"kind":"text","text":" defames and judges the law. If you judge the law, you are not a doer of the law but a judge. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 7:1","book":"Mat","chapter":7,"verse":1,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jms 1:22","book":"Jas","chapter":1,"verse":22,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 2:1","book":"1Pe","chapter":2,"verse":1,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 7:1","book":"Mat","chapter":7,"verse":1},{"label":"Jms 1:22","book":"Jas","chapter":1,"verse":22},{"label":"1Pt 2:1","book":"1Pe","chapter":2,"verse":1}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or his brother or sister"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:4:12","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"There is one lawgiver and judge "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Other mss omit and judge"},{"kind":"text","text":" who is able to save and to destroy. But who are you to judge your neighbor? "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 10:28","book":"Mat","chapter":10,"verse":28,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 14:4","book":"Rom","chapter":14,"verse":4,"letter":"b"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 10:28","book":"Mat","chapter":10,"verse":28},{"label":"Rm 14:4","book":"Rom","chapter":14,"verse":4}],"footnotes":[{"marker":2,"text":"Other mss omit and judge"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:4:13","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Come now, you who say, “Today or tomorrow we will travel to such and such a city and spend a year there and do business and make a profit.” "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Pr 27:1","book":"Pro","chapter":27,"verse":1,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 12:18–20","book":"Luk","chapter":12,"verse":18,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Pr 27:1","book":"Pro","chapter":27,"verse":1},{"label":"Lk 12:18–20","book":"Luk","chapter":12,"verse":18}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:4:14","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Yet you do not know what tomorrow will bring —what your life will be! For you are like vapor that appears for a little while, then vanishes. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jb 7:7","book":"Job","chapter":7,"verse":7,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 102:3","book":"Psa","chapter":102,"verse":3,"letter":"b"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jb 7:7","book":"Job","chapter":7,"verse":7},{"label":"Ps 102:3","book":"Psa","chapter":102,"verse":3}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:4:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Instead, you should say, “If the Lord wills, we will live and do this or that.” "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:4:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But as it is, you boast in your arrogance. All such boasting is evil. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 18:21","book":"Act","chapter":18,"verse":21,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 5:6","book":"1Co","chapter":5,"verse":6,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 18:21","book":"Act","chapter":18,"verse":21},{"label":"1Co 5:6","book":"1Co","chapter":5,"verse":6}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:4:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"So it is sin to know the good and yet not do it. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 12:47–48","book":"Luk","chapter":12,"verse":47,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 9:41","book":"Jhn","chapter":9,"verse":41,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Pt 2:21","book":"2Pe","chapter":2,"verse":21,"letter":"c"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lk 12:47–48","book":"Luk","chapter":12,"verse":47},{"label":"Jn 9:41","book":"Jhn","chapter":9,"verse":41},{"label":"2Pt 2:21","book":"2Pe","chapter":2,"verse":21}],"footnotes":[]}]},"cachedAt":1783279682525}